CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.31
-------------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o CoOncoplot - Plot two oncoplots side by side
    o rainfallPlot
    o oncoplot now supports copy number data
    o New function readGistic to read summarize output files from GISTIC.
    o dashboard style plot for mafsummary
    o Plotting functions for GISTIC results: plotGisticResults, gisticPlot
    o geneCloud to plot wordcloud of frequently mutated genes and copy number alteartions.

SIGNIFICANT USER-LEVEL CHANGES

    o More plotting parameters to plotCBSsegments.

BUG FIXES

    o Bug fix while performing fisher exact for differences between cohorts.

DEPRECATED AND DEFUNCT

    o Remove AddReadcounts function, which relied on extrenal patform specific parogram bam-readcount

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.30
-------------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o Plotting and mapping variants on copy number data (require cbs segments)
    o Compare two maf files for differentially mutated genes
    o Forestplots
    o Better clustering with copynumber and outlier detection for heterogeneity.


CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.25
-------------------------

NEW FEATURES
    o inferHeterogeneity: Clustering using nonparametric dirichlet process; more plotting options.
    o New subsetMaf function to subset MAF

SIGNIFICANT USER-LEVEL CHANGES
    o Fixed a warning in oncodrive function
    o Upto 5X faster oncomatrix creation and sorting using data.table
    o Examples won't take >5 seconds
    o Updated vignette

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.20
-------------------------

CHANGES:
    o Resubmission to bioconductor using r-devel 3.3


